message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper is about using deep neural networks for organ segmentation in medical images, specifically abdominal CT scans. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, since the focus is on medical imaging, it could also belong to the medical imaging (cs.MED) sub-category. Finally, since deep neural networks are used, it could also belong to the neural networks (cs.NEURON) sub-category.
